        </p>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem;">
          <div style="text-align: center; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 1rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; min-width: 110px;">
            <p style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #FFFFFF; margin: 0;">100%</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin: 0.25rem 0 0;">Führungsleidenschaft</p>
          </div>
          <div style="text-align: center; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 1rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; min-width: 110px;">
            <p style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #FFFFFF; margin: 0;">+330</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin: 0.25rem 0 0;">Mitarbeiter entwickelt</p>
          </div>
          <div style="text-align: center; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 1rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; min-width: 110px;">
            <p style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #FFFFFF; margin: 0;">+29</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin: 0.25rem 0 0;">Jahre Führung &amp; Management</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="flex-shrink: 0;">
        <img src="/leadership/marcus-about.jpeg" alt="Marcus Eichler – Coaching"
          style="width: 260px; height: 320px; border-radius: 1rem; object-fit: cover; border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust Logos (repeat) -->
